T1  - Asymptotic Efficiency in Parametric Structural Models with Parameter-Dependent Support
AU  - Hirano, Keisuke
AU  - Porter, Jack R.
Y1  - 2003/09/01
PY  - 2003
DA  - 2003/09/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/1468-0262.00451
